        What Is a Put and Call Option on Property in Queensland?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A put and call option deed is a legal arrangement used in Queensland property transactions, particularly by developers and investors. Here is what sellers need to understand before signing one.
      </p>
